      "value": "<p><span style=\"font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\"><strong>Adaptable Persona </strong>(transmutation) Armor only. When you manifest the essence form, gain your choice of a climb Speed or swim Speed equal to your land Speed. If you're 8th level or higher, you can choose a fly Speed instead. <em style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;scrollbar-width:auto !important;scrollbar-color:initial;color:rgb(231, 209, 177);font-family:Roboto, sans-serif;font-size:17.5px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgba(6, 4, 3, 0.92);text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial\">Corruption Flaw</em> You take a -10-foot penalty to all your Speeds.</span></p>",
